  <description><![CDATA[<p>The lovely and traditional Hotel Alaska is a family run property in the centre of resort and just 150 metres from the ski lifts connecting you to the Costaccia gondola. Run by the Bormolini family, their aim is for guests to enjoy a homely and relaxing setting at an affordable price. Rooms are clean and comfortable, everything you need for your weeks skiing holiday, particularly good for couples or even small groups.   </p>
<p>Just a stone throw away and you are in the vibrant pedestrianised centre of <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/italy/livigno">Livigno</a> where you can enjoy browsing the shops, popping into a cafe for a coffee or after a day out on the mountain you can enjoy some of the many great bars and après the resort has to offer. </p>
<p>If you are looking for something a little quieter and a bit more relaxing, the hotel bar is a great place to enjoy a beer or glass of wine with friends and family, or to unwind and get lost in a good book before you tuck into the delights served in the restaurant. </p>]]></description>
