  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Alaska sits just off the central streets of Livigno. Shops, cafes and bars are all close by as is the lifts which are just 150 metres away. Good value for money, a  comfortable setting and service make this a great option for couples and small groups who want to visit one of the great up and coming ski resorts in Europe.</p>]]></listingDescription>
